  "text": "Relations between the kinetic energy spectrum and the second order velocity structure function were derived in two dimensions. These are related to those given by [CITATION_1] but are specifically applicable to longitudinal structure functions, which are easily measured with pairs of particles. The relations involve Hankel transforms, and can be evaluated with routines found in Matlab.",
