    "119937545": {
      "title": "Relative dispersion: local and nonlocal dynamics",
      "abstract": "Abstract Observations of relative dispersion statistics for stratospheric balloons, including velocity structure functions, relative diffusivities and separation kurtoses, are shown to be consistent with nonlocal dynamics rather than local, self-similar dynamics."
